  "description": "<p><strong>Role: Project & Technical Sales Engineer</strong></p><p><strong>Industry: Safety Engineering Solutions</strong></p><p><strong>Location: Kaki Bukit </strong></p><p><strong>5 days | Mon-Fri: 9am to 6pm </strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $3600 to $7000 + Bonus</strong></p><p><strong></strong><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Possess Electrical Engineering educational qualification</strong></li><li><strong>Relevant working experience in Engineering & onboard vessel site services. </strong></li><li><strong>Knowledge of PAGA, CCTV, PABX, Fire Alarm Systems, Fire & Gas systems, Helideck lightings systems, Weather Monitoring systems, Aids to Navigation systems, Instruments, added advantage</strong>.</li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities：</strong></p><ul><li>Autocad Drawings and project documentation</li><li>Project administration and scheduling</li><li>Technical Sales proposal and clarifications with customers</li><li>Project engineering and design</li><li>Hands-on product integration , troubleshooting, testing, etc. </li><li>Site Services on board vessel (local & overseas)</li></ul><p>Tai Jia Seng Reg No: R26159755</p><p>The Supreme Hr Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
